details.options: [Bag holds approx. 15 items:Upgrade tote to larger canvas shopping bag][What is Your Desired Delivery Date?:Deliver ASAP][Message:Dear Briana Irene Wright Happy Valentines day to someone who is more than just special to me. Of the countless times and nights we%27d stay up talking on the phone or even in person, you never got bored and cared for what i had to say; you really heard me. For the first time in my life i thought wow, ive never had so much in common with someone and especially someone that was also very passionate, smart and really caring. I didnt know what to do. So i tried getting to know you better. Time passed and we became best friends. Then one day i asked you out. At first you told me no. I didnt understand why, so i asked again hoping you would say yes. You said no. This time i had to ask why. You said you didnt want to ruin us. I said it wouldnt be ruining us if we were together, it would mean we wouldnt be ruined but closer to eachother in a deeper way. Finally you said ok. I said what do you mean ok? Briana Irene Wright will you go out with me? You said yes. Other than the first time i saw you, i wont forget that night, the night my bestest friend became my partner and the person i love. You have been wondering what it is that i love about you for some time now and i cant put all of it into words but let me try to name off a few, i love the way you laugh and smile, the way you tap your foot when you%27re mad. I love the way you get excited when you talk to me about things. I love the way you get mad at people and give them your piece of mind when they do anything concerning animals. I love the way you get scared over any kindof bug and i get to make you feel better putting it outside. I love the way you go out of your eay to do things for those who cant and even snails who cant and try to protect them too. I love the way you laugh, sing around the house, and i love that i get to wake up to you every single day next to me. You are more amazing with each day that passes and you mean way more to me than you think. Happy Valentines day my Alien Mermaid Princess Briana.
